19f97f93 [deepseek-chat] #
19f97f93 [deepseek-chat] #
19f97f93 [deepseek-chat] #• 2. Pattern Recognition (more reliable):*
19f97f93 [deepseek-chat] #- Look for sequence: 5 equalizing → 5 broad → 5 equalizing pulses
19f97f93 [deepseek-chat] #- Count 5 long pulses within ~10 lines
19f97f93 [deepseek-chat] #
19f97f93 [deepseek-chat] #• 3. Combined HSYNC/VSYNC detection:*
19f97f93 [deepseek-chat] #
19f97f93 [deepseek-chat] #// State machine approach
