19f98b32 [deepseek-chat] #- Uses standard PAL timings (625 lines total, 50 Hz)
19f98b32 [deepseek-chat] #- But displays all 288 active lines every field (non-interlaced)
19f98b32 [deepseek-chat] #- Each field is identical = progressive scan
19f98b32 [deepseek-chat] #- Still follows PAL sync structure with serrated VSYNC
19f98b32 [deepseek-chat] #
19f98b32 [deepseek-chat] #• Why not 50P?*
19f98b32 [deepseek-chat] #- 50P typically means 576p50 (full frame progressive)
19f98b32 [deepseek-chat] #- VIC-20 has only 288 visible lines per field
