19f98b32 [deepseek-chat] #
19f98b32 [deepseek-chat] #• Signal characteristics:*
19f98b32 [deepseek-chat] #- 50 fields/second (identical content each field)
19f98b32 [deepseek-chat] #- 288 active lines per field
19f98b32 [deepseek-chat] #- Uses same sync pulses as interlaced PAL
19f98b32 [deepseek-chat] #- CRT displays it as stable non-interlaced image
19f98b32 [deepseek-chat] #
19f98b32 [deepseek-chat] #• Technical term:* "288-line progressive scan at 50 Hz using PAL timings" or simply "PAL
