19f9e279 [nitro@ryzen5] describe the serrated VSYNC
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #• Serrated VSYNC* is the unique vertical sync pulse structure used in interlaced video
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #standards like PAL and NTSC.
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #• Structure (PAL example):*
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #Line 1:  |-----|     |-----|     (equalizing pulses)
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #Line 2:  |-----|     |-----|
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #Line 3:  |-----|     |-----|
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #Line 4:  |-----|     |-----|
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #Line 5:  |-----|     |-----|
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #Line 6:  |-----------|           (broad pulse - 27.3µs)
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #Line 7:            |-----------|
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #Line 8:  |-----------|
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #Line 9:            |-----------|
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #Line 10: |-----------|
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #Line 11: |-----|     |-----|     (equalizing pulses)
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #Line 12: |-----|     |-----|
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #etc...
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #• Key features:*
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #1. 5 equalizing pulses (normal HSYNC width: ~4.7µs)
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #2. 5 broad pulses (double width: ~27.3µs) over 2.5 lines
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #3. Another 5 equalizing pulses
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #4. Total: ~20 lines for complete VSYNC sequence
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #• Why serrated?*
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #- Maintains horizontal sync during vertical blanking
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #- Prevents horizontal oscillator from drifting
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #- Ensures proper interlace alignment (odd/even fields)
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #• Electrical characteristics:*
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #- Pulses are negative-going like HSYNC
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #- Broad pulses = 2× normal HSYNC width
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #- Equalizing pulses = normal HSYNC width
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #- Occurs during vertical blanking interval
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #• Detection clue:* Look for 3+ consecutive broad pulses during expected vertical interval
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #(every 312.5 lines in PAL).
19f9e382 [deepseek-chat] #
