19fa020a [deepseek-chat] #- CRT vertical oscillator synchronization
19fa020a [deepseek-chat] #
19fa020a [deepseek-chat] #• So yes:* 288 visible + 24.5 vblank = 312.5 lines per field, matching PAL half-frame
19fa020a [deepseek-chat] #timing while displaying progressive content.
