1a818cea [gemini-3.1-pro] #vertical sync pulse. 576i technically requires "equalizing pulses" (short pulses at twice the
1a818cea [gemini-3.1-pro] #horizontal frequency) during the vertical blanking interval. This keeps the CRT's horizontal
1a818cea [gemini-3.1-pro] #oscillator stable during the half-line shift.
