1a8afb8e [claude-opus-4-6] #extra pins on the same cycle.
1a8afb8e [claude-opus-4-6] #
1a8afb8f [claude-opus-4-6] #In this case every instruction both does its job (out data, jmp, set) AND sets the BCK and WSEL
1a8afb8f [claude-opus-4-6] #pins:
1a8afb8f [claude-opus-4-6] #
1a8afb8f [claude-opus-4-6] #
