1a8afb90 [claude-opus-4-6] #
1a8afb90 [claude-opus-4-6] #
1a8afb91 [claude-opus-4-6] #Without side-set you'd need separate instructions to toggle the clocks, doubling the program length
1a8afb91 [claude-opus-4-6] #and halving the speed.
1a8afb91 [claude-opus-4-6] #
1a8afb91 [claude-opus-4-6] #The `.side_set 2` directive reserves 2 bits of the delay/side-set field for this. That costs you 2
1a8afb92 [claude-opus-4-6] #bits of available delay (max delay drops from 31 to 7) but for I2S you don't need delays.
1a8afb92 [claude-opus-4-6] #
