1aaecfc9 [gemini-3.1-pro] #single line, you must wrap the object in parentheses `({ ... })`. Otherwise, the engine interprets
1aaecfc9 [gemini-3.1-pro] #the curly braces `{}` as the start of a function block rather than an object.
