1aaecfc9 [gemini-3.1-pro] #Because the updated version expands the arrow function into a multi-line block to add the
1aaecfca [gemini-3.1-pro] #`try/catch` logic, we switch to using standard function braces `{ ... }` and an explicit `return {
1aaecfca [gemini-3.1-pro] #... }` statement. That is why the outer parentheses are no longer needed.
